name: Tramonto
description:
I made it the traditional way, using knives and glue. I combined paper after paper to make it this.

This shows that we will not only be happy to live in this world. There must be sadness, pleasure, happiness, or whatever. This I dedicate to you who got this nft.

I will hold an auction for this, if the winner is still in the territory of Indonesia, I will send the physical goods to the winner.
